{"userId":"G2AKPKwR4mSQXOI6","title":"HELLO WORLD","description":"Before bidding farewell to this beautiful world, she looked back towards the future.\nLight bathes the world, as people welcome rebirth through their tears.\nNo more regrets, no more goodbyes. All will meet, embrace, and grow until their lives become one with the cosmos.\nYeah, those are the days to come that the Remembrance will never get to experience firsthand.\nBut she believes that the Trailblaze will carry the past forward unto eternity.\nOn this final page, with all the love in the world, she drew a \"◦\" for causality.\nLike rippling waves in an endless loop, waiting in the years of yesterday.\nLike a trailblazing compass, guiding tomorrow's endless march forward.\n\n※ We recommend viewing this video after experiencing Version 3.7 Trailblaze Mission.\nInterlude: Ripples of Past Reverie\nSinger: Cassie Wei from Mili\n\nEnglish Voice:\nCyrene — Aiden Dawn\n\nDownload the Game\nhttps://hoyo.link/cVcmAcxP1\n\nFollow us to get the latest info.\nHoYoLAB: https://www.hoyolab.com/accountCenter...\nFacebook:   / honkaistarrail  \nX:   / honkaistarrail  \nDiscord:   / discord  \nInstagram:   / honkaistarrail  \nTikTok:   / honkaistarrail_official  \nReddit:   / honkaistarrail  \n\n#HonkaiStarRail\n#StarRail\n#Cyrene","youtubeUrl":"https://youtu.be/LB_65-rOYYo?list=RDLB_65-rOYYo","videoId":"LB_65-rOYYo","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/LB_65-rOYYo/hqdefault.jpg","category":"","views":0,"likes":[],"dislikes":[],"createdAt":1778727775944,"_id":"XCmsu5ecythKCw6H"}
